<span class="line"><span>}</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>```</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id="自定义容器" tabindex="-1">自定义容器 <a class="header-anchor" href="#自定义容器" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;自定义容器&quot;">​</a></h3><div class="tip custom-block"><p class="custom-block-title">TIP</p><p>这是一个提示信息。</p></div><div class="warning custom-block"><p class="custom-block-title">WARNING</p><p>这是一个警告信息。</p></div><h3 id="代码行高亮" tabindex="-1">代码行高亮 <a class="header-anchor" href="#代码行高亮" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;代码行高亮&quot;">​</a></h3><div class="language- vp-adaptive-theme"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang"></span><pre class="shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark vp-code" tabindex="0"><code><span class="line"><span>```js{4}</span></span>
